snippet.title: Push - Rain of Reflections (Original Game Soundtrack)
snippet.description:
"Push" is an original composition by Jonatan Järpehag for the Rain of Reflections soundtrack, featured in the recently released "story trailer" for the game.

See the trailer at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7axU-PbZuY.

The song can also be found on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/6IODWLGl0Hb9a2eGFcdQOs

Learn more about Rain of Reflections at http://rainofreflections.com.
